{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "7a8542b9-70b4-4581-98e8-27fb979a0b64",
    "name": "Banking Agent MCP Server Standard PoC",
    "description": "Spring Boot 기반 Banking Agent MCP Server PoC 요청 모음입니다.\n\n## 실행 전제\n- `docker compose up --build -d`\n- MCP Server: `{{MCP_BASE_URL}}`\n- Mock Legacy Service: `{{LEGACY_BASE_URL}}`\n- Worker Service: `{{WORKER_BASE_URL}}`\n- Prometheus: `{{PROMETHEUS_URL}}`\n- Grafana: `{{GRAFANA_URL}}`\n\n## Mock 인증\n- USER: `{{USER_API_KEY}}`\n- ADVISOR: `{{ADVISOR_API_KEY}}`\n- ADMIN: `{{ADMIN_API_KEY}}`\n\n## 권장 확인 순서\n1. System / MCP Server Health\n2. MCP JSON-RPC / tools/list\n3. MCP JSON-RPC / resources/list\n4. MCP JSON-RPC / resources/read - account schema\n5. MCP JSON-RPC / prompts/list\n6. MCP JSON-RPC / prompts/get - customer consulting summary\n7. MCP JSON-RPC / account_summary\n8. MCP JSON-RPC / customer_ticket_create\n9. MCP JSON-RPC / loan_product_recommend - Access Denied\n10. Async Job / customer_ticket_create_async\n11. Async Job / async_job_status\n12. Ops API / Audit Events\n13. Ops API / Jobs\n14. Mock Legacy API / Account Summary\n15. Monitoring / Prometheus UI\n16. Monitoring / Grafana UI\n\n모든 데이터는 포트폴리오용 mock 데이터이며 실제 금융사명, 실제 고객명, 실제 계좌번호, 실제 업무 전문을 포함하지 않습니다.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
